{
  "texts": [
    "In their studies, participants were presented with a series of cues for future events and were instructed to imagine the events going well or poorly for 3 min.",
    "Participants were instructed that each imagined event should occur within the next year.",
    "Afterwards, participants were given descriptions of how the events happened.",
    "In a second session, participants were tested for their memory of how the event happened.",
    "Across two studies, future simulations from older and younger adults were audio-recorded, transcribed, and scored according to the interview."
  ]
}